considered especially heinous.

00:12.246 --> 00:14.615
In New York City,
the dedicated detectives

00:14.648 --> 00:16.450
who investigate
these vicious felonies

00:16.484 --> 00:18.219
are members of an elite squad
known as

00:18.252 --> 00:19.953
the Special Victims Unit.

00:19.987 --> 00:21.789
These are their stories.

00:23.391 --> 00:24.958
Sorry, watch those blocks.

00:24.992 --> 00:27.328
So what, that toy box
is just what, decorative?

00:27.361 --> 00:29.663
Oh, you brought the jokes.

00:29.697 --> 00:30.664
Listen, would you hold him
for a minute?

00:30.698 --> 00:32.633
Huh?
Ah, oh.

00:32.666 --> 00:34.835
Thanks.

00:34.868 --> 00:39.173
So you said you didn't want to
talk about this in the office?

00:39.207 --> 00:43.911
Um, Johnny D, the pimp,
he's still in custody

00:43.944 --> 00:45.679
on federal charges?

00:45.713 --> 00:48.649
