to break them in.

01:35.229 --> 01:40.168
Look, I haven't slept
since I...

01:40.168 --> 01:42.670
Just tell me that he doesn't
have to know.

01:42.703 --> 01:44.772
He doesn't.

01:44.805 --> 01:48.476
It's not exculpatory in any way.
He never needs to find out.

01:48.509 --> 01:52.346
