the adoption paperwork.

01:52.380 --> 01:56.217
Given Noah's early history,
how can you be expected

01:56.250 --> 01:58.786
to know who his father was?

02:09.197 --> 02:13.066
Walter?
Excuse me.

02:13.100 --> 02:17.538
They dig you out of the old
novelist's home for this too?

02:19.473 --> 02:20.908
It's Fred Worth, Walter.

02:20.941 --> 02:23.377
Fred Worth.
Wow, great to see you.

02:23.411 --> 02:25.213
