slice off my ears

02:36.224 --> 02:37.958
and mail them to the Viet Cong.

02:37.991 --> 02:39.760
I didn't do it.
Did I?

02:39.793 --> 02:41.562
Of course not, darling.

02:41.595 --> 02:44.232
I guess you're going strong,
Walter.

02:44.232 --> 02:47.501
Forgot what it takes to hold
onto a beauty like this.

02:47.535 --> 02:50.103
My prettiest wife yet.

02:50.137 --> 02:52.640
Oh, look, there's Roland Evans.

02:52.673 --> 02:54.942
Ah.
Fred, great to see you.

02:54.975 --> 02:58.346
Great to see you too.

03:04.252 --> 03:05.986
- Dad!
- Dad?

03:06.019 --> 03:08.356
