for the party because of her.

03:08.389 --> 03:09.390
- Charmaine?
- Yeah, Dad.

03:09.423 --> 03:10.824
She won't let us see you.

03:10.858 --> 03:12.660
Delilah, please not now.
Your father is cold.

03:12.693 --> 03:14.862
We've been to the house.
She hasn't let us in to see you.

03:14.895 --> 03:17.097
Dad--Dad, we just want to know
are you all right?

03:17.130 --> 03:18.432
- We miss you.
- Yeah, I--I'm great.

03:18.466 --> 03:20.000
