03:20.033 --> 03:21.402
Dad, are you sure?

03:21.435 --> 03:23.571
- I'm fine.
- Watch your head.

03:23.604 --> 03:24.905
Dad?

03:24.938 --> 03:26.574
It was great to see you.

03:36.284 --> 03:37.751
[knock at door]

03:37.785 --> 03:39.287
Hey, Sarge, there's two women

03:39.287 --> 03:41.389
