to someone in charge.

03:41.422 --> 03:43.791
Sure.

03:43.824 --> 03:45.693
Hi, how can I help you?

03:45.726 --> 03:47.895
We want to report
a sex crime--a rape.

03:47.928 --> 03:51.965
Oh, I'm so sorry.
Why don't you have a seat?

03:51.999 --> 03:54.535
- Which one of you--
- It wasn't one of us.

03:54.568 --> 03:57.305
It was our father,
Walter Briggs.

03:57.305 --> 04:00.107
The novelist?
I'm a huge admirer.

04:00.140 --> 04:01.809
I've read every one
of his books ever since--

04:01.842 --> 04:04.312
So what happened to him?

04:04.312 --> 04:05.846
His wife, Charmaine,

04:05.879 --> 04:08.148
