of erectile dysfunction pills

04:08.181 --> 04:10.951
and makes him have sex
every day, which is dangerous,

04:10.984 --> 04:12.686
considering
he's got a heart condition.

04:12.720 --> 04:15.389
He's divorced
from both our mothers.

04:15.423 --> 04:17.157
Charmaine won't let us see him.

04:17.190 --> 04:18.826
So how do you know this?

04:18.859 --> 04:20.728
His housekeeper told us.

04:20.761 --> 04:23.831
She feels terrible,
but she doesn't know what to do.

04:23.864 --> 04:26.334
That may not technically
be rape.

04:26.334 --> 04:30.571
Penal law section 130.25--
sexual intercourse with a person

04:30.604 --> 04:33.407
who is incapable of consent
because of mental disability

04:33.441 --> 04:35.242
or incapacitation.

04:35.343 --> 04:38.579
Our father is almost 80
and has dementia.

04:38.612 --> 04:39.647
He does not consent.

04:39.680 --> 04:41.715
He cannot consent.

04:41.749 --> 04:43.050
Did you look that up?

04:43.083 --> 04:44.485
- I'm in law school.
- Oh, where?

04:44.518 --> 04:48.856
- I'm in Fordham--nights.
- Carisi?

04:48.889 --> 04:51.224
Why would she be doing this?

04:51.258 --> 04:53.827
Our father's will divides
his estate in equal shares

04:53.861 --> 04:56.530
between his current wife
and his children.

04:56.564 --> 05:00.468
Your stepmother wants a child
so she can have an extra share.

05:00.501 --> 05:03.136
So she's raping him.

05:10.444 --> 05:13.414
[dramatic music]

05:13.447 --> 05:21.422
