is legally irrelevant

07:03.691 --> 07:06.660
but, I mean,
of all the people--I mean,

07:06.694 --> 07:08.962
have you guys read Briggs' book
The Fifth Assailant?

07:08.996 --> 07:10.664
The guy is a literary genius.

07:10.698 --> 07:12.800
