07:21.842 --> 07:22.976
What's in it for them?

07:23.010 --> 07:24.878
A bigger slice of the estate?

07:24.912 --> 07:27.347
No--love, devotion,
maybe concern?

07:27.380 --> 07:28.882
Right.

07:28.916 --> 07:30.651
We've got an allegation,
we have corroborations,

07:30.684 --> 07:34.154
so you two go speak
with the happy couple.

07:34.187 --> 07:35.222
And Carisi,

07:35.255 --> 07:38.792
as a detective, not a fan.

07:43.096 --> 07:45.298
I should say I'm still
not quite sure why you're here.

07:45.332 --> 07:46.867
It's called a welfare check.

07:46.900 --> 07:49.002
