what happens to your testicles.

08:45.993 --> 08:47.928
Roman Follies.
It was a wonderful book, sir.

08:47.961 --> 08:49.597
- I read it in college.
- Thank you.

08:49.630 --> 08:50.798
All of his books
are wonderful.

08:50.831 --> 08:52.299
Okay, so Mr. Briggs,

08:52.332 --> 08:53.867
