11:04.998 --> 11:06.734
Of course I have 12 crazies
here today.

11:06.734 --> 11:08.201
I'm a playwright.

11:08.235 --> 11:10.470
I started this theater
to put up my own work,

11:10.503 --> 11:12.039
so now I'm artistic director,

11:12.072 --> 11:14.541
fundraiser, ticket taker,
occasional janitor.

11:14.574 --> 11:16.376
