that clear.

12:49.302 --> 12:50.437
Yeah, plus the rape
and assault charges

12:50.470 --> 12:52.172
are still under investigation.

12:52.205 --> 12:53.941
Barely--one of them's a stretch,
the other one's a chasm.

12:53.974 --> 12:55.843
