getting dragged across the city.

12:55.843 --> 12:57.244
Well, we're not social workers.

12:57.277 --> 13:00.080
But we are cops,
and we can keep investigating.

13:00.113 --> 13:02.850
- Knock yourselves out.
- We will.

13:09.022 --> 13:10.590
Mommy?
Yeah, it's me.

13:10.623 --> 13:12.993
