13:23.937 --> 13:25.672
The dispatcher said
you handled a call today

13:25.705 --> 13:27.875
concerning a patient
named Briggs.

13:27.875 --> 13:29.877
The sick old dude
with the crazy wife?

13:29.877 --> 13:31.111
You tell me.

13:31.144 --> 13:33.046
Guy had tubes
hanging out of his arms.

13:33.080 --> 13:34.781
